She grinned... purred ... as she returned the favor, kissing him more. The 
future seemed to be so in their favor. Whatever the Tripred mentioned about 
Alpha Trion's plans for her... she quickly cast them aside. Didn't appear that it 
would ever happen. & Alpha Trion.. would once again fail. It brought warmth to 
her lasercore at the thought that the Autobots & their pathetic Maximal 
decendents would no advance.
